<h3><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f9ee.png" alt="ğŸ§®" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> CÃ´ng thá»©c tÃ­nh RSI:</h3>
<p>RSI = 100 âˆ’ [100 / (1 + (Lá»£i nhuáº­n trung bÃ¬nh / Thua lá»— trung bÃ¬nh))]</p>
<p>Ã nghÄ©a thÃ nh pháº§n:</p>
